        protected double cluster(DataSet data,
             int[] medioids,
             int[] assignments)
        Description copied from class: PAM
        Performs the actual work of PAM.
        Overrides:
        cluster in class PAM
        Parameters:
        data - the data set to apply PAM to
        medioids - the array to store the indices that get chosen as the medoids. The length of the array indicates how many medoids should be obtained.
        assignments - an array of the same length as data, each value indicating what cluster that point belongs to.
        Returns:
